{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526520/extras/Page_Text4.png?t=1730574086\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526520/extras/Gameplay.gif?t=1730574086\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The flickering torchlight and cold steel in your hand are your only defenses against the total, devouring darkness that surrounds you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will know the true meaning of fear as you hear the cries of twisted abominations encircling you in the inky blackness. Your only hope is to collect and call on the unearthly powers of the Deck and to become an unstoppable force.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are an artifact hunter, a seeker and purveyor of rare, magical relics. Your profession takes you into some of the darkest and most dangerous recesses of existence. The ultimate goal of your search is the fabled Deck of Darkness, an incredibly potent arcane artifact said to grant it's bearer immortality\u2026 for a price. Survive long enough and you will face your terrifying destiny in the dungeon's darkest depths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Deck of Darkness: Infernal Depths</i> is an atmospheric, retro, dark fantasy horror action role-playing game. Think one part 3D Diablo, one part Hexen, and one part Nethack and all old-school dungeon crawl with crunchy, pixel-art graphics. Being a roguelike dungeon crawler, every playthrough will be unique. Each level has it's own theme and monsters, which become more fearsome as you go deeper. Make it to the lowest level of the dungeon and face your terrifying destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Most dungeon crawlers are brightly lit cakewalks compared to this one. Luckily, the powers of the Deck will make you a formidable foe indeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><